ExpressionView.SQL: select ISO2, REGION, NAME from BASE_COUNTRY, CATEGORY where BASE_COUNTRY.ISO2 = CATEGORY.COUNTRY AND DTYPE = 'CountryRegion' and REGION <> 'Uncategorized'
SELECT ID, LABEL FROM CATEGORY WHERE DTYPE='CountryIncomeStatus'

select * from GLOBAL_CUBE WHERE GLOBAL_DESIGNATION != 'DOCO' AND GLOBAL_DESIGNATION in (select iso2 from BASE_COUNTRY) AND GLOBAL_DESIGNATION in (select v.designation from v_cp_validated_designations v where v.entity_year = GLOBAL_ENTITY_YEAR)
